  "title": "Vibrant Savory Filipino Wild Garlic Leaves Dinuguan",
  "description": "A savory Filipino dish featuring wild garlic leaves in a rich and spicy bhuna sauce, served with a side of steamed rice for a comforting solo dinner.",
