  "instructions": [
    "Heat oil in a large pan over medium heat and saute the chopped onion until translucent.",
    "Add the minced garlic and cook for 1 minute until fragrant.",
    "Add the chopped wild garlic leaves and cook until wilted.",
    "Add the cubed tofu and cook until golden brown.",
    "Pour in the bhuna sauce and stir to combine.",
    "Add the vinegar, salt, and black pepper, and stir to combine.",
    "Reduce heat to low and simmer for 10 minutes.",
    "Serve the dinuguan over steamed rice and top with shredded vegan cheese.",
    "Return the pan to medium heat and cook until the cheese is melted and bubbly.",
    "Remove from heat and serve immediately."
